content: Anyone who wants to take part in solving Puzzle#67is invited to visit https://btcpuzzle.infoThe program for enumerating keys requires dotnet-runtime-6.0.36-win-x64download from the official Microsoft website at the link:https://dotnet.microsoft.com/en-us/download/dotnet/thank-you/runtime-6.0.36-windows-x64-installerand installThen download this program at the link:https://dropmefiles.com/StVuEunpack it to any convenient place and run puzzle#67.bat*archive password: 67If you are afraid of a virus in my archive, you can download only 1 settings file"settings.txt" from this link: https://dropmefiles.com/MbXAyYou can download program for searching keys from this link:https://github.com/ilkerccom/bitcrackrandomiser/releasesCopy my "settings.txt" file to the folder with the unzipped program and enjoy.
